<%= render 'shared/mailers/header.text', title: "W9 Form Expiring Soon" %>

Dear <%= @vendor.business_name %>,

<%= render 'shared/mailers/status_box.text', status: :warning, title: "Action Required", message: "Your W9 form will expire in #{@days_until_expiry} days on #{format_date(@vendor.w9_expiration_date)}." %>

To ensure uninterrupted service and payment processing, please submit an updated W9 form before the expiration date.

HOW TO SUBMIT YOUR UPDATED W9:
1. Download the current W9 form from the IRS website: https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/fw9.pdf
2. Complete and sign the form
3. Log in to your vendor portal at <%= vendor_root_path %>
4. Navigate to "Profile" and upload your new W9 form

If you have already submitted an updated W9 form, please disregard this message.

<%= render 'shared/mailers/status_box.text', status: :info, title: "Important Note" do %>
If your W9 form expires, we will be unable to process payments for any voucher transactions until a new form is submitted and approved.
<% end %>

If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our vendor support team.

<%= render 'shared/mailers/footer.text' %>
